1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 1=

21
00:01:48,040 --> 00:01:49,000
Who's there?

22
00:01:54,790 --> 00:01:55,760
What's this place?

23
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:13,960
I am you.

24
00:02:15,630 --> 00:02:17,080
It must be a dream.

25
00:02:18,020 --> 00:02:19,700
("Once an Empress"
Filming Begins Soon)

26
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:20,820
(Fan Buzz Alert #TreasureBoy)
An Jingyu.

27
00:02:20,820 --> 00:02:21,680
(An Jingyu stars as the 14th Prince)
For you,

28
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:23,870
I even finished reading this cheesy

29
00:02:23,870 --> 00:02:24,720
cliché palace novel.

30
00:02:24,730 --> 00:02:25,570
So you have to…

31
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:27,680
No, wait…

32
00:02:52,300 --> 00:02:54,820
(Shen Zhaodi / Ye Jin)

33
00:03:06,590 --> 00:03:08,030
What the hell is this place?

34
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:17,000
By order of Consort Lan,

35
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:19,800
escort the guilty maid Ye Jin to her death.

36
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:22,000
No, wait. Ye Jin?

37
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:22,840
What consort?

38
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,050
Hey, keep your hands off me.

39
00:03:24,050 --> 00:03:24,730
Explain yourself.

40
00:03:24,730 --> 00:03:25,910
The guilty maid Ye Jin,

41
00:03:25,910 --> 00:03:28,560
your murder of Lady Qiu Yu is proven.

42
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:30,120
Stop playing dumb.

43
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:31,840
Ye Jin?

44
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,750
(Isn't that the throwaway maid)

45
00:03:33,750 --> 00:03:35,450
(who dies in Chapter One?)

46
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:37,120
(I got transmigrated?)

47
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:39,150
(Why her, of all people?)

48
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,150
Hands off.

49
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,120
It hurts.

50
00:03:43,310 --> 00:03:44,470
So I'm in a novel, huh?

51
00:03:45,030 --> 00:03:45,890
Fine.

52
00:03:45,890 --> 00:03:47,040
Don't blame me

53
00:03:47,070 --> 00:03:48,630
when my cheats wreck it all.

54
00:03:48,750 --> 00:03:50,150
The real killer is…

55
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:53,960
Take her away.

56
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:54,800
I…

57
00:03:58,980 --> 00:04:01,820
(Consort Lan)

58
00:04:02,020 --> 00:04:03,940
(Consort Duan, Lady Fucha)

59
00:04:07,430 --> 00:04:08,630
What's wrong?

60
00:04:09,710 --> 00:04:10,550
Your Highness,

61
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:13,190
Consort Duan's ride is blocking the way.

62
00:04:21,950 --> 00:04:23,720
Forgive me, Consort.

63
00:04:24,270 --> 00:04:26,630
I'm with child.

64
00:04:26,950 --> 00:04:29,630
It's inconvenient to step down and bow.

65
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:32,390
You're so "precious" now.

66
00:04:32,950 --> 00:04:35,240
I wouldn't dream of it.

67
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:38,390
I heard the Empress Dowager is unwell

68
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:42,000
and came to visit.

69
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:43,830
But why are you

70
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,870
only arriving now?

71
00:04:47,190 --> 00:04:49,800
I manage the entire harem.

72
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,160
I'm busy.

73
00:04:51,390 --> 00:04:53,950
I'm not as free as you.

74
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:57,950
Now your sedan blocks the gate,

75
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:00,720
are you expecting me to take a detour?

76
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:05,040
The Empress Dowager allowed me to ride in

77
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:08,600
because of the pregnancy.

78
00:05:09,510 --> 00:05:12,830
We just happened to cross paths

79
00:05:13,310 --> 00:05:16,160
and I stopped to pay my respects.

80
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:19,600
I didn't mean to inconvenience you.

81
00:05:19,830 --> 00:05:21,920
I'm so sorry.

82
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:23,560
Biqing.

83
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,480
Help me down.

84
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:27,720
Walking a few steps

85
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:30,040
shows my devotion.

86
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,850
Look at her arrogance.

87
00:05:53,280 --> 00:05:55,920
She thinks she can outrank you

88
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:57,120
just because she's carrying?

89
00:05:57,190 --> 00:05:59,270
A child for status?

90
00:05:59,950 --> 00:06:02,280
Let her enjoy it while it lasts.

91
00:06:03,260 --> 00:06:04,420
The hour has come.

92
00:06:04,660 --> 00:06:06,820
Your worthless life ends now.

93
00:06:08,340 --> 00:06:09,940
Wait!

94
00:06:10,590 --> 00:06:12,250
I'm pregnant with the 14th Prince's child!

95
00:06:12,900 --> 00:06:13,940
What did you say?

96
00:06:14,090 --> 00:06:15,820
You're about to die and you're still lying?

97
00:06:16,020 --> 00:06:17,900
I said I'm pregnant!

98
00:06:19,380 --> 00:06:21,460
Who among you can take responsibility

99
00:06:21,900 --> 00:06:23,540
for killing a royal heir?

100
00:06:29,180 --> 00:06:31,420
(The 14th Prince)

101
00:06:31,860 --> 00:06:33,260
Pardon us, Your Highness.

102
00:06:34,620 --> 00:06:35,460
Mm.

103
00:06:51,980 --> 00:06:52,820
Your Highness.

104
00:06:53,460 --> 00:06:54,310
Your Highness.

105
00:06:54,380 --> 00:06:55,970
The Department of Justice brought a maid.

106
00:06:56,100 --> 00:06:56,940
She claims...

107
00:06:57,340 --> 00:06:58,820
she's carrying your child.

108
00:07:00,180 --> 00:07:01,020
Absurd.

109
00:07:01,580 --> 00:07:04,340
I've been here to attend to the sick
for less than two weeks.

110
00:07:04,780 --> 00:07:05,660
Exactly.

111
00:07:05,940 --> 00:07:08,300
What a clumsy attempt

112
00:07:08,780 --> 00:07:09,940
to ruin your reputation.

113
00:07:10,860 --> 00:07:11,780
Bring her in.

114
00:07:11,970 --> 00:07:12,810
Yes, sir.

115
00:07:12,860 --> 00:07:13,700
Enter.

116
00:07:20,780 --> 00:07:21,620
Kneel.

117
00:07:26,900 --> 00:07:27,820
You?

118
00:07:28,460 --> 00:07:29,820
Carrying my child?

119
00:07:31,100 --> 00:07:31,940
I...

120
00:07:33,940 --> 00:07:35,180
An Jingyu?

121
00:07:36,180 --> 00:07:37,020
An Jingyu.

122
00:07:37,020 --> 00:07:38,020
(An Jingyu stars as the 14th Prince)
For you,

123
00:07:38,020 --> 00:07:40,220
I even finished reading this cheesy

124
00:07:40,220 --> 00:07:41,260
cliché palace novel.

125
00:07:41,780 --> 00:07:42,620
How did you

126
00:07:42,820 --> 00:07:43,700
transmigrate too?

127
00:07:44,020 --> 00:07:44,860
How dare you?

128
00:07:44,860 --> 00:07:46,060
The Prince is questioning you.

129
00:07:46,460 --> 00:07:47,300
An Jingyu,

130
00:07:47,460 --> 00:07:48,500
I'm your fan.

131
00:07:48,660 --> 00:07:50,080
I'm a member of your fan club.

132
00:07:50,110 --> 00:07:51,380
Last month in Hong Kong, China,

133
00:07:51,380 --> 00:07:52,380
we were cheering you on.

134
00:07:54,260 --> 00:07:55,100
Your Highness,

135
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:56,540
this woman is insane.

136
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:57,920
There's no point

137
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:59,540
in questioning her further.

138
00:07:59,540 --> 00:08:00,380
Take her away

139
00:08:00,500 --> 00:08:01,900
and deal with her.

140
00:08:02,210 --> 00:08:03,140
No, wait.

141
00:08:03,140 --> 00:08:03,980
Your Highness.

142
00:08:04,580 --> 00:08:05,420
Get out.

143
00:08:07,500 --> 00:08:08,340
Move.

144
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,320
Your Highness,

145
00:08:09,380 --> 00:08:10,580
I know your secret.

146
00:08:10,660 --> 00:08:11,500
On your lower back,

147
00:08:11,500 --> 00:08:12,900
there's a red birthmark

148
00:08:12,900 --> 00:08:13,920
shaped like a maple leaf.

149
00:08:14,020 --> 00:08:16,140
A fortune-teller said it's a sign of destiny.

150
00:08:20,900 --> 00:08:21,940
Who are you?

151
00:08:22,080 --> 00:08:23,100
Doesn't matter who I am.

152
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:24,060
Just know that I can

153
00:08:24,060 --> 00:08:25,140
cure the Empress Dowager.

154
00:08:25,180 --> 00:08:26,380
She's going to faint soon,

155
00:08:26,380 --> 00:08:27,900
and it'll happen more and more often.

156
00:08:28,300 --> 00:08:29,500
Trust me, I can cure her.

157
00:08:29,500 --> 00:08:30,580
Please. Show mercy.

158
00:08:32,220 --> 00:08:34,540
Your Highness.
The Empress Dowager fainted again.

159
00:08:35,500 --> 00:08:36,700
Trust me.

160
00:08:37,020 --> 00:08:37,860
Please.

161
00:08:38,380 --> 00:08:39,940
Please, Your Highness.

162
00:08:40,060 --> 00:08:41,220
Your Highness.

163
00:08:41,220 --> 00:08:42,220
Please. Trust me.

164
00:08:42,220 --> 00:08:43,620
Please, Your Highness.

165
00:08:43,700 --> 00:08:44,540
Your Highness.

166
00:08:48,740 --> 00:08:50,220
(The Empress Dowager)

167
00:08:50,220 --> 00:08:51,420
How is my mother's condition?

168
00:08:52,940 --> 00:08:54,140
Your Majesty,

169
00:08:54,380 --> 00:08:57,020
Her Highness has suffered
from diabetes for long.

170
00:08:57,660 --> 00:08:59,180
These frequent faints are a sign

171
00:08:59,660 --> 00:09:01,900
of worsening condition

172
00:09:01,900 --> 00:09:04,220
and depleted vitals.

173
00:09:04,220 --> 00:09:05,260
(The Emperor)
Is there truly

174
00:09:05,540 --> 00:09:06,700
no cure at all?

175
00:09:07,140 --> 00:09:08,940
Diabetes has always been difficult.

176
00:09:09,300 --> 00:09:11,420
There is no permanent cure.

177
00:09:11,660 --> 00:09:12,620
For now,

178
00:09:12,620 --> 00:09:14,260
only management.

179
00:09:14,740 --> 00:09:17,700
Her Majesty loves sweets

180
00:09:17,700 --> 00:09:18,900
and dislikes physical activity.

181
00:09:19,220 --> 00:09:20,180
Both are fatal

182
00:09:20,180 --> 00:09:21,820
for this illness.

183
00:09:22,180 --> 00:09:24,140
We've advised her many times,

184
00:09:24,460 --> 00:09:25,460
but the Empress Dowager

185
00:09:25,940 --> 00:09:27,260
refuses to listen.

186
00:09:27,260 --> 00:09:28,120
I am truly

187
00:09:28,130 --> 00:09:30,860
at my wits' end.

188
00:09:36,220 --> 00:09:37,260
Who are you?

189
00:09:37,500 --> 00:09:38,520
Doesn't matter who I am.

190
00:09:38,620 --> 00:09:39,500
Just know that I can

191
00:09:39,500 --> 00:09:40,700
cure the Empress Dowager.

192
00:09:45,420 --> 00:09:46,940
I studied medicine for eight years,

193
00:09:47,860 --> 00:09:49,540
finally made it

194
00:09:50,420 --> 00:09:52,900
and took over the family clinic.

195
00:09:54,100 --> 00:09:56,700
How did I suddenly

196
00:09:57,100 --> 00:09:58,620
become a throwaway maid

197
00:09:58,620 --> 00:10:01,740
who dies instantly?

198
00:10:06,020 --> 00:10:07,860
God, help me.

199
00:10:09,140 --> 00:10:11,460
I learned medicine to save lives,

200
00:10:12,300 --> 00:10:14,820
not to die as a scapegoat.

201
00:10:16,620 --> 00:10:18,500
It can't be.

202
00:10:25,820 --> 00:10:27,380
(Isn't that the superstar Zhao Mi?)

203
00:10:27,820 --> 00:10:28,900
(Did she transmigrate too?)

204
00:10:29,340 --> 00:10:30,660
(No. That's not right.)

205
00:10:30,780 --> 00:10:32,540
(Zhao Mi's acting was never this natural.)

206
00:10:32,980 --> 00:10:34,700
(She's the role Zhao Mi plays.)

207
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:35,560
(Zhi Hui.)

208
00:10:35,560 --> 00:10:36,810
(Zhi Hui)
I remember you said

209
00:10:36,820 --> 00:10:39,060
you love lotus root patties
and ginger chicken from home.

210
00:10:40,180 --> 00:10:41,260
I made these myself.

211
00:10:42,420 --> 00:10:43,260
Here.

212
00:10:47,020 --> 00:10:47,860
Eat while it's warm.

213
00:10:53,580 --> 00:10:54,540
Well, thank you

214
00:10:55,060 --> 00:10:56,940
for the last meal.

215
00:10:57,540 --> 00:10:58,540
Don't talk like that.

216
00:10:58,660 --> 00:11:00,020
I'll try to save you.

217
00:11:01,260 --> 00:11:03,100
In novels,

218
00:11:03,100 --> 00:11:05,300
I hate the innocent act most.

219
00:11:06,500 --> 00:11:08,020
You let the villains do all the work

220
00:11:08,380 --> 00:11:09,780
and after you get what you want,

221
00:11:09,780 --> 00:11:11,260
you act all poor and innocent.

222
00:11:11,740 --> 00:11:13,580
Ye Jin died with a grievance,

223
00:11:13,580 --> 00:11:15,700
and you were nowhere to be seen.

224
00:11:15,700 --> 00:11:17,500
And now you show up,
acting like some saint?

225
00:11:18,580 --> 00:11:19,820
Eat up, it's hot.

226
00:11:23,380 --> 00:11:25,180
Why are you looking at me?

227
00:11:26,420 --> 00:11:27,420
(Can she not hear me?)

228
00:11:27,740 --> 00:11:28,860
(Anything unrelated)

229
00:11:29,180 --> 00:11:31,860
(or disruptive will be blocked?)

230
00:11:35,540 --> 00:11:37,060
Do you know who the killer is?

231
00:11:38,300 --> 00:11:39,180
I don't.

232
00:11:39,180 --> 00:11:40,020
I do.

233
00:11:40,580 --> 00:11:41,580
The killer

234
00:11:41,740 --> 00:11:43,380
is you.

235
00:11:47,800 --> 00:11:50,230
♪I am but an outsider♪

236
00:11:50,250 --> 00:11:52,440
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

237
00:11:52,660 --> 00:11:56,700
♪Outwit the world but not the way we meet♪

238
00:11:56,700 --> 00:12:00,940
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

239
00:12:05,220 --> 00:12:08,470
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

240
00:12:08,640 --> 00:12:12,030
♪In a world of lies, you're all that's clear♪

241
00:12:12,030 --> 00:12:14,540
♪I know how this story ends♪

242
00:12:14,540 --> 00:12:19,110
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

243
00:12:19,410 --> 00:12:23,550
♪Truth or lie—I can't tell♪

244
00:12:28,500 --> 00:12:31,810
♪You hide it all behind your lines♪

245
00:12:31,810 --> 00:12:35,090
♪So familiar, yet out of reach♪

246
00:12:35,290 --> 00:12:38,370
♪A history that no one can search♪

247
00:12:38,640 --> 00:12:41,900
♪Like you drift in from another star♪

248
00:12:41,950 --> 00:12:43,700
♪I am but an outsider♪

249
00:12:43,700 --> 00:12:45,940
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

250
00:12:45,940 --> 00:12:50,000
♪Outwit the world but not the way we meet♪

251
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:54,650
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

252
00:12:58,580 --> 00:13:01,980
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

253
00:13:01,980 --> 00:13:05,340
♪In a world of lies, you're all that's clear♪

254
00:13:05,340 --> 00:13:07,810
♪I know how this story ends♪

255
00:13:07,810 --> 00:13:12,000
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

256
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:15,270
♪When it's over and I'm gone♪

257
00:13:15,270 --> 00:13:19,060
♪Please forget me and move on♪

258
00:13:19,060 --> 00:13:25,300
♪Just let this absurd dream fade♪

259
00:13:28,460 --> 00:13:36,820
♪Snow hides our tracks♪

260
00:13:40,390 --> 00:13:50,110
♪When do I finally wake♪
